A6.text: The National Front (NF) is a far-right, fascist political party in the United Kingdom. It is currently led by Tony Martin.

A7.text: Founded in 1967, it reached the height of its electoral support during the mid-1970s, when it was briefly England's fourth-largest party in terms of vote share.
